text:
Amana, you know~
I'm called Amana~.

Naa-chan...?
Were you talking to someone?

Yeah,
she's swimming really well right now.

Oh, really...!
Hehehe... dolphin-san, it's cute, isn't it?

Yeah~
That's why I told Amana that too, that she's cute.

...
Next time... I might tell Tenka too, huh?

It would be nice if they come back here again...
Ah――!
